{"tid":2517350,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"劉丹力撐吳偉豪冇做錯 只係交友不慎：我哋都後生過","createTime":"2021-05-05T09:17:02.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T09:24:59.000Z","uid":130626,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3a65250b9e4e608ca6753c1802f117c0f872299c","tid":2517350,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:17:02.000Z","msg":"劉丹今天（5日）出席TVB處境喜劇《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》宣傳母親節活動，談到母親節，丹爺覺得很好笑，每年這個節日都會有人送花給他：「好奇怪，有時候我送花畀人，又有人會送花畀我，但都係一個開心節日。」<br />\n<br />\n近日TVB藝人吳偉豪不雅影片流出，外界有種種傳聞，有傳因此事會被TVB雪藏，甚至會被踢出劇集《愛&middot;回家之開心速遞》，丹爺都知道有這件事情發生，力撐吳偉豪沒有錯：「我成日都講一句，朱凌凌（吳偉豪）根本冇做錯，只不過係交友不慎。同埋講真呀，我哋都後生過，成日都想問吓年輕人自己有冇做過呀，都冇人夠膽話冇，咁咪係囉，大家都知咩事，只不過佢唔好彩。大家講啲鼓勵說話，將事情慢慢丟淡佢，然後再重新投入工作。」<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210505/466628911342555136791350.jpeg/blnA3ERGZwFbRdNL1Q3oEvhRS0cDGtJnqygpk6soKZM?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210505%2F466628911342555136791350.jpeg%2FblnA3ERGZwFbRdNL1Q3oEvhRS0cDGtJnqygpk6soKZM%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bef77793&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e19693c7d63577efec664dc5680e0a45b0ca5b07","tid":2517350,"uid":59868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:18:32.000Z","msg":"咁似之前個劇本既<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25b9f9c4df59cfd6779a9c900e7fadfafcaeb198","tid":2517350,"uid":149266,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:19:16.000Z","msg":"成日都想問吓年輕人自己有冇做過呀，都冇人夠膽話冇<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n夠膽自拍咁短嘅賓洲仲send比人 的確唔係個個做到"},{"pid":"4fa054b13183909a9d86bb72a3de6bcc9e2cbcd6","tid":2517350,"uid":5655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:19:29.000Z","msg":"教壞細路"},{"pid":"b5da92e22e237ec3727d34a9ea9a4c3c0c3a793a","tid":2517350,"uid":165352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:21:30.000Z","msg":"直接幫佢認撚左<br />\n<br />\n直接幫00認左碌尻咁細"},{"pid":"ce67672197bdcf9d69b2164863e4bbf4fbc0575b","tid":2517350,"uid":391165,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"我懷疑佢無俾錢<br />\n所以先流出"},{"pid":"cf7cf0a53b81d94a9a441dd03e637938f798c7b7","tid":2517350,"uid":190789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:21:47.000Z","msg":"劉丹有無睇過前新抱段片？我有老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a19a3d2ab85085f202998a31fd17407be127b6b","tid":2517350,"uid":90455,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T09:24:59.000Z","msg":"叉燒炳後生嘅時候都試過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}